<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />古代的文字，<delay8 />有着独特的浪漫风情～！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过我一个字也看不懂！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实，<delay20 />就算用我看得懂的文字，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />写成这样<delay8 />密密麻麻、看起来内容深奥的文章，<delay20 />
我应该也读不懂它的意思<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">胜利女神啊～<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />究竟<delay8 />长着什么样的脸呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定长得很像我呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～！<delay20 />它好像马上就要动起来一样！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让人完全想不到<delay8 />这是石头制成的！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay frames="30" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />让人不知道该看哪儿好<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">有很多人<delay8 />喜欢这幅画呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家是不是<delay8 />都喜欢这样的笑容啊？<delay frames="30" />
<colour id="5" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />微、<delay20 />微笑！<colour id="65535" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好漂亮的画啊～～～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎么说呢，<delay8 />比如<delay20 />它的色彩<delay8 />什么的，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还有<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总之就是很漂亮啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />让人很有身临其境的感觉呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉像要被带入画中的世界了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这孩子<delay8 />看起来年纪还很小，<delay20 />
但是很有气质呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这将来肯定<delay8 />会成为大人物的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇！<delay20 />好帅啊～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也想像这样，<delay20 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
率领着大家前进！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅画<delay8 />让人感觉有些悲伤呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我能进入这画中的世界，<delay20 />
我一定会尽力救她的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座岛<delay8 />现实生活中也有吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有点想去，<delay20 />又有点不敢去。<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅画<delay20 />近看就是
一个个五颜六色的点！<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay20 />拉远距离再看<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶～！<delay20 />为什么？！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为什么会这样？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅画不仅很漂亮，<delay20 />还很神奇呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一直看着它，<delay20 />
好像会被吸进画中的世界！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这幅画虽然很小，<delay8 />但是好有气势啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果有绣着这种图案的棒球夹克，<delay20 />
应该非常帅吧<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这墓中<delay8 />真是放了<delay20 />
好多好多雕像啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难道是这座墓的主人害怕孤单吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个还真是让人<delay20 />越看越喜欢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一开始看到它<delay8 />完全没什么感觉，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看久了便觉得它挺可爱的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔，<delay frames="30" />创作者到底在思考些什么，<delay20 />
才造出了这么一尊思考者的雕塑？<delay frames="40" />
唔<delay frames="5" />～<delay frames="5" />～<delay frames="5" />～<delay frames="5" />～<delay frames="5" />～<delay frames="5" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听说，<delay8 />这是你赠予博物馆的？<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你竟能得到这么棒的东西，<delay20 />太厉害了吧！<delay frames="40" />
真是个了不起的家伙啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀！<delay frames="40" />
<size value="75" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />忘记不能喧哗了。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<size value="100" /></message>
</msbt>